Because outside of Platonism-Neoplatonism this - all this qua realms/levels of ontology not just of thinking - is impossible or does not exist, is noncommunicative (i.e. "Rome AD 45 + USA 1974 are both here + now equally"). I grasped [the category of] essence + it is real; more, this is how reality is in fact arranged. I could grasp the category of essence + see that A + B were on the essence level one-+-the-same, but I could not then extrapolate to the Essence (Form) real

